      "title": "GenAsset load workflow notes",
      "properties": {},
      "widgets_values": [
        "# GenAsset load workflow\n\nFill these fields:\n\n- `base_url`: `https://genasset.xyz` (or your local GenAsset URL)\n- `token`: from GenAsset `Settings -> Tokens`\n- `asset_id`: exact asset UUID (optional)\n- `version_id`: exact version UUID (optional)\n\nLoad modes:\n\n- Exact version: set `version_id`.\n- Latest for one asset: leave `version_id` empty and set `asset_id`.\n- Latest in workspace: leave both empty.\n\nWhere to find ids:\n\n- `asset_id`: asset page -> copy asset id, or `Save To GenAsset` output `asset_id`.\n- `version_id`: version history -> copy version id, or `Save To GenAsset` output `version_id`.\n\nIf preview shows a tiny black 64x64 image, check `status_json.error` and verify `base_url` + `token` target the same workspace as the ids."
      ],
      "color": "#243",
      "bgcolor": "#355"
    }
